    cdm.fixml.datatypes.LocalMktDate

typeAlias LegSettlRateFallbackReferencePage_t: <"Identifies the reference \"page\" from the rate source.  When LegSettlRateFallbackRateSource(40366) = 3(ISDA Settlement Rate Option) this contains the value from the scheme that reflects the terms of the Annex A to the ISDA 1998 FX and Currency Option Definitions. See: http://www.fpml.org/coding-scheme/settlement-rate-option">
    string

typeAlias PaymentStreamNonDeliverableSettlReferencePage_t: <"Identifies the reference \"page\" from the rate source.  When PaymentStreamNonDeliverableSettlRateSource(40371) = 3(ISDA Settlement Rate Option) this contains the value from the scheme that reflects the terms of the Annex A to the ISDA 1998 FX and Currency Option Definitions. See: http://www.fpml.org/coding-scheme/settlement-rate-option">
    string

