    int

typeAlias PaymentStreamFixingDateBusinessCenter_t: <"The business center calendar used to adjust the payment stream\'s fixing date, e.g. \"GBLO\".  See http://www.fpml.org/coding-scheme/business-center for standard 4-character code values.">
