    number

typeAlias LegDeliveryStreamTotalPositiveTolerance_t: <"The positive percent tolerance which applies to the total quantity delivered over all shipment periods.  Percentage value is to be expressed relative to \"1.0\" representing 100% (e.g. a value of \"0.0575\" represents 5.75%.).">
