typeAlias LegDeliveryStreamCommoditySource_t: <"The SCoTA coal cargo origin, mining region, mine(s), mining complex(es), loadout(s) or river dock(s) or other point(s) of origin that seller and buyer agree are acceptable origins for the coal product. For international coal transactions, this is the origin of the coal product.  See http://www.fpml.org/coding-scheme/commodity-coal-product-source for values.">
