typeAlias LegPaymentStreamCompoundingInitialRate_t: <"The initial compounding floating rate reset agreed between the principal parties involved in the trade. It should only be included when the rate is not equal to the rate published on the source implied by the floating rate index. The initial rate is expressed in decimal form, e.g. 5% is represented as \"0.05\".">
    cdm.fixml.datatypes.Percentage

typeAlias LegPaymentStreamCompoundingFinalRatePrecision_t: <"Specifies the compounding floating rate rounding precision in terms of a number of decimal places. Note how a percentage rate rounding of 5 decimal places is expressed as a rounding precision of 7.">
