    string

typeAlias ReturnRateReferencePage_t: <"Identifies the reference \"page\" from the rate source.  For FX, the reference page to the spot rate to be used for the reference FX spot rate.  When ReturnRateInformationSource(42762) = 3 (ISDA Settlement Rate Option) this contains the value from the scheme that reflects the terms of the Annex A to the ISDA 1998 FX and Currency Option Definitions.  See: http://www.fpml.org/coding-scheme/settlement-rate-option">
    string

